headline: Polymarket's Customer Data Sought by CFTC Subpoena of Coinbase, Source Says
summary: The U.S. Commodity Futures Trading Commission is said to be seeking information about customers' interactions with the prediction market site Polymarket.

headline: Bitcoin falls to lowest level since November as Trump rally loses steam in inauguration run-up
summary: Bitcoin (BTC-USD) fell more than 3% Thursday to just over $92,000 — its lowest level since November.

headline: Coinbase Notifies Users of CFTC Subpoena Related to Polymarket Investigation
summary: Coinbase has reportedly been served with a subpoena from the Commodity Futures Trading Commission (CFTC) concerning the crypto prediction market platform Polymarket.

headline: Three Reasons to Avoid COIN and One Stock to Buy Instead
summary: Coinbase’s 18.9% return over the past six months has outpaced the S&P 500 by 12.8%, and its stock price has climbed to $261.45 per share. This run-up might have investors contemplating their next move.
